node.text:
5 rounds
30 seconds burpee 
30 second jump squats 
30 second pike push ups
30 second  half walk outs 
60 second rest

Hit that link in the bio to get your spot for my 30 day Full body HIIT challenge. This program going for its final round tomorrow Monday April 26. Hit the link in the bio to save your spot before it closes tonight.

Enjoy over 50 body weight exercises with modifications, written along with video instructions, meal planning, an accountability group of other challengers, and mobility exercises all at home.

Look out for the new challenge coming soon!

node.text:
And when life hits hard sometimes you must hit back 10x harder.

Told myself let’s get up!

#getupandmove #fullbodywork #strongwoman #workhard

Less talking more working brings about progress for certain!

Focused on the things I can control and allowing God to handle the rest. Moving this body while I’m able and pushing myself to be my absolute best.

Saturdays Stretch!

Nothing like some great partner mobility work with @d.butlerfit on a Saturday.

Big thank you to everyone who came out to the HIIT class this morning and those who tuned in virtually. We will keep you guys updated on when the next class is so keep a lookout!

Outfit: @myfitbymoefit

#partnermobility #partnerstretch #partnerworkout

node.text:
On your journey to a greater you one must understand that everyone isn’t conditioned to make it or experience growth. You must be willing to remove yourself from old habits, old situations, and leave some people behind.

How bad do you want it?
Learn from them and embrace those growing pains

Some snippets of the other days upper body work

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Monique Collier on July 14, 2021 tagging @buffbunny_collection. May be an image of 2 people and people standing.

node.text:
Always strive for a better you but at every level embrace and love all of you!

Outfit: @buffbunny_collection

HIIT was today’s move!

 30 seconds for each move 
Knock out all 5 moves no breaks in between 
45 second rest after all 5 moves

Click the link in my bio and lock in your spot for our HIIT class this Saturday at 9:30am

This full body HIIT class will be a tough one(with modifications). @D.butlerfit and I are going have you working like no other with moves that will build and sculpt muscle, torch fat, and test athleticism. 

#fullbodyworkout #HIIT #HIITworkout #stayconsistent #move

node.text:
Happy Monday!

Show up and show out today for yourself. Set the tone and start your week strong!

Tickets for our HIIT Class on July 17 are now live for in person and for live streaming. HIIT the link in my bio and secure your spot.

Started the week with some partner kettle bell work. Tag a friend and get into these moves

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Monique Collier on July 02, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and standing.

node.text: Take care of your body but invest in your peace of mind…. We are all deserving of happy times.

node.text:
Full body Friday’s in full effect.

It has been a productive week full of blessings and joy. A few hiccups here and there but everything was handled just as quick as it came. I’m excited for the weekend and the new things that are about to come. I hope you all enjoy your weekend and don’t forget to get it in before you head out this evening.

My 30 day full body burn HIIT program will be going for another round on July 5. Hit that link above and be sure to lock in your spot.
Enjoy over 50 body weight exercises with modifications, written along with video instructions, meal planning, an accountability group of other challengers, and mobility exercises all at home.
